== SOURCE

https://becominghuman.ai/how-netflix-uses-ai-and-machine-learning-a087614630fe

== AGENT

Netflix

== GOAL

Recommend Movies and TV to Customers

== DATA

They use users recation to other things they watch, Collected from the users past viewing 

== METHODS

Supervised learning 

== RESULTS

The more you watch on netflix the more accurate the recommendations are 

== ISSUES

Keeping past data on customer, Smaller movie titles get left behind as they are not watched as often 

== SCORE

7

== COMMENTS

Interesting to see how netflix keep your data in datasets to train their AI on making recommendations for future watching #